<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ wǒ lái dào nǐ miàn qián 迦南370</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ wǒ lái dào nǐ miàn qián, xīn zhōng hé děng hé děng gān měi,
 cóng wèi yǒu guò de píng ān, jū zhù zài wǒ xīn lǐ,
 wǒ de zhǔ a, wǒ yào xiàng nǐ yǎng liǎn,
 wǒ de shén a, wǒ yào xiàng nǐ yǎng liǎn.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>370</hymn_number>
</song>